Package com.xebialabs.overthere.util

Contains a number of utility classes for users of the Overthere library.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ByteArrayFile OverthereFile backed by a byte array.
CapturingOverthereProcessOutputHandler An implementation of the OverthereProcessOutputHandler that captures the output in variables.
ConsoleOverthereProcessOutputHandler Implementation of the OverthereProcessOutputHandler interface that prints the output to the console (System.out and System.err).
LoggingOverthereProcessOutputHandler Implementation of the OverthereProcessOutputHandler interface that sends the output to the specified logger.
MultipleOverthereProcessOutputHandler Implementation of the OverthereProcessOutputHandler interface that sends the output to one or more other handlers.
OverthereFileCopier OverthereFile copy utility that uses only the input and output streams exposed by the OverthereFile to perform the copying action.
OverthereFileDirectoryWalker Abstract class that walks through a directory hierarchy and provides subclasses with convenient hooks to add specific behaviour.
OverthereUtils Contains a number of static helper methods.
 

Package com.xebialabs.overthere.util Description

Contains a number of utility classes for users of the Overthere library.
